# Dummy line chart placeholder
highchart() %>%
  hc_chart(type = "line") %>%
  hc_title(text = "Placeholder Trend (static)") %>%
  hc_xAxis(categories = month.abb) %>%
  hc_add_series(name = "Trend A", data = sample(10:100, 12)) %>%
  hc_add_series(name = "Trend B", data = sample(50:120, 12))

df %>%
  arrange(desc(resilience_score)) %>%
  hchart("bar", hcaes(x = company, y = resilience_score)) %>%
  hc_title(text = "Resilience Scores by Company") %>%
  hc_yAxis(title = list(text = "Score")) %>%
  hc_xAxis(title = list(text = "Company")) %>%
  hc_colors("#4CAF50")
highchart() %>%
  hc_chart(type = "pie") %>%
  hc_title(text = "Category Distribution (Placeholder)") %>%
  hc_add_series(
    name = "Categories",
    data = list_parse2(data.frame(
      name = c("Red", "Blue", "Green"),
      y = c(30, 50, 20)
    ))
  )

# Gauge Chart for Selected Company
highchart() %>%
  hc_chart(type = "solidgauge") %>%
  hc_title(text = paste("Resilience Score –", params$company)) %>%
  hc_pane(
    center = list("50%", "85%"),
    size = "140%",
    startAngle = -90,
    endAngle = 90,
    background = list(
      backgroundColor = "#EEE",
      innerRadius = "60%",
      outerRadius = "100%",
      shape = "arc"
    )
  ) %>%
  hc_yAxis(
    min = 0,
    max = 5,
    title = list(text = "Score"),
    stops = list(
      list(0.2, "#DF5353"),
      list(0.5, "#DDDF0D"),
      list(0.8, "#55BF3B")
    ),
    lineWidth = 0,
    tickInterval = 1,
    labels = list(y = 16)
  ) %>%
  hc_add_series(
    name = "Score",
    data = list(selected_score),
    tooltip = list(valueSuffix = " / 5")
  )
